name: Crash Landing
Lore: 'AT-AT weapons are rarely quick enough to score a direct hit on a fastmoving snowspeeder. They are more likely to wing a craft, causing a forced landing.',
Text: 'If you have a piloted AT-AT present at a site, target opponent''s non-creature vehicle present at same or adjacent exterior site. Draw destiny. If AT-AT has a vehicle weapon, add 1 to destiny draw. Target ''crashes'' if total destiny > 3.',
